item.title: Need help with PI
item.dc:creator: @Mariokillu Mariokillu
item.description:
@Mariokillu wrote:

For Project Insanity, the commands would be in Commands.java.

You can find the in src\server\model\players\packets.

As for the item code list, go into Data/cfg and open Item.cfg. Theres your item list.

Welcome to Project Insanity, if you have any questions, feel free to private message me.
